The paper is about a large-scale multi-modal dataset for face anti-spoofing, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The dataset includes RGB, Depth, and IR modalities, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and image processing (cs.IR). The goal of face anti-spoofing is to prevent security breaches, which is related to computer security (cs.CR).
